            "entrance_animation": true
          },
          "image_role": "decorative",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/intro-1.png",
            "alt": "Intro_1.png",
            "source_asset": "Intro_1.png",
            "mime_type": "image/png",
            "bytes": 93469,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 222
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "subheading",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "heading_html": "<p>在本模块结束时，您将能够：</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "list",
          "variant": "bulleted",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "list_style": "bulleted",
          "items_html": [
            "<p>解释向 ORW 的过渡及其对 AI 效率和可扩展性的影响。 &nbsp;</p>",
            "<p>确定ORW结构、有效负载选项、兼容性和可持续性特征。 &nbsp;</p>",
            "<p>定义电源完整性、100A 排序和高功率机架共享基线。</p>"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "divider",
          "variant": "divider",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p>随着人工智能需求的加速，标准的600毫米机架造成了严重的<strong>物理瓶颈</strong>。本模块探讨 OCP 社区 &nbsp; 如何响应 1200 毫米 ORW 框架。</p><p>您将了解该标准如何发展，通过更智能的电力传输、稳健的结构设计和可扩展的基础设施来满足下一代要求。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "hero",
          "style": {
            "image_size": "large",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": true,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "image_role": "content",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/x-8dc63f.jpg",
            "alt": "一个标准架和ZQQT0QXZ的宽度比较.",
            "source_asset": "X-#8DC63F.jpg",
            "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
            "bytes": 115597,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1343,
              "originalHeight": 1080
            }
          },
          "caption_html": "<p><em>Embed影像标签:标准架,600毫米;Open Rack Wide(ORW),1200毫米;物理宽度增加,600毫米;可容纳较大的计算;集成液冷却. 兹哈兹哈兹哈兹"
        },
        {
          "id": 7,
          "type": "quote",
          "variant": "d",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "LIGHT",
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "quote_html": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 2.1rem\"><em>特别感谢 AMD 的 PMTS 系统架构师 Eduardo Estrada 提供的技术指导和意见，这对本课程的开发起到了重要作用。</em></span></p>",
