          "style": {
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p style=\"line-height: 1.15\">ORW基本规范旨在为大规模部署提供通用框架，同时最大限度地提高兼容性和可持续性。</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.15\">单击标记探索Open Rack Wide框架的核心结构和功能。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "labeled_graphic",
          "variant": "labeledgraphic",
          "style": {
