          "body_html": "<p>向高密度 AI 机架供电需要强大的电气连接。 ORW 框架使用标准化接口来安装 48V 母线，确保与高功率机架共享基线的无缝互操作性。</p><p>单击每个选项卡了解更多信息。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "accordion",
          "variant": "accordion",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "zoom_on_click": false,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "title": "标准化母线安装",
              "description_html": "<p>用于母线安装的框架接口与 ORV3 HPR 母线接口相同。</p>",
              "media": {
                "path": "resources/images/untitled-design-49.jpg",
                "alt": "Untitled design (49).png",
                "source_asset": "Untitled design (49).jpg",
                "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                "bytes": 100049,
                "dimensions": {
                  "width": 1680,
                  "height": 944,
                  "originalWidth": 1680,
                  "originalHeight": 1680
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "100A 连续电源路径",
              "description_html": "<p>IT Gear 输入连接器具有主电源路径和电源返回路径，其额定连续电流至少为 100A。</p>",
              "media": {
                "path": "resources/images/untitled-design-50.jpg",
                "alt": "Untitled design (50).png",
                "source_asset": "Untitled design (50).jpg",
                "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
                "bytes": 38421,
                "dimensions": {
                  "originalWidth": 1680,
                  "originalHeight": 1680
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "电源排序和传感",
              "description_html": "<p>新连接器要求 IT 设备设计使用电源检测线来控制电源输入电路的开和关行为，防止危险的电弧事件。</p>",
              "media": {
                "path": "resources/images/it-gear-input-connector.png",
                "alt": "IT Gear Input Connector.png",
                "source_asset": "IT Gear Input Connector.png",
                "mime_type": "image/png",
                "bytes": 33471,
                "dimensions": {
                  "originalWidth": 541,
                  "originalHeight": 512
                }
              }
            },
            {
              "title": "差分电压检测",
              "description_html": "<p>这个可选但强烈推荐的功能允许设施监控输入电源电缆组件的电压降，从而增强热事件缓解。</p>"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
