    {
      "id": 6,
      "slug": "knowledge-check",
      "title": "知识检查",
      "description_html": "",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "type": "text",
          "variant": "paragraph",
          "style": {
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "body_html": "<p style=\"line-height: 1.94118\"><span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: inherit\" data-color-scope=\"outer\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><span>测试本模块的知识。为每个问题选择最佳答案，然后提交。</span></span></span></span></p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "type": "image",
          "variant": "full",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "LIGHT",
            "card_mode": "WHITE",
            "image_opacity": 0.5,
            "image_opacity_color": "#000000",
            "zoom_on_click": false,
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 0,
            "padding_bottom": 0,
            "custom_padding_top": 0,
            "custom_padding_bottom": 0,
            "entrance_animation": true
          },
          "image_role": "decorative",
          "media": {
            "path": "resources/images/black-banner-intro-1.png",
            "alt": "Black banner - intro.png",
            "source_asset": "Black banner - intro-1.png",
            "mime_type": "image/png",
            "bytes": 12283,
            "dimensions": {
              "originalWidth": 1680,
              "originalHeight": 295
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>为什么 ORW 基本规格从机架设计中消除了标准滚动脚轮？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>为更大的液体冷却歧管腾出空间。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>直接在结构平台上安全支撑高达 3,500 公斤的重量。</p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>确保与较旧的 19 英寸 IT 设备兼容。</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>降低底座的整体制造成本。</p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正确！由于满载的 ORW 机架重达 3,500 公斤，因此标准脚轮不再是安全的选择。机架直接位于结构平台上，以实现最大稳定性。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>标准脚轮会在 3,500 公斤的人工智能集群的巨大重量下弯曲。 ORW 框架设计为直接位于结构平台上。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>对还是错？ Open Rack Wide 框架仅支持 OpenU 垂直间距。</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>真</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>假</p>",
              "correct": true
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正确！ ORW 框架支持 OU 和 RU 垂直间距。它包括用于支撑支架的特定切口，以允许混合各种类型的 IT 设备。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正确。基本规范要求 ORW 框架必须通过不同的支架支持 OU 和 RU 垂直间距。</p>"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "type": "knowledge_check",
          "variant": "multiple_choice",
          "style": {
            "background_type": "COLOR",
            "background_color": "#1e1e1e",
            "attached_to_next": false,
            "padding_top": 3,
            "padding_bottom": 3
          },
          "question_type": "multiple_choice",
          "question_html": "<p>Open Rack V3 IT 齿轮输入连接器上的主电源和返回路径的最小连续额定电流是多少？</p>",
          "choices": [
            {
              "text_html": "<p>200A连续</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>150A连续</p>",
              "correct": false
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>100A连续</p>",
              "correct": true
            },
            {
              "text_html": "<p>50A连续</p>",
              "correct": false
            }
          ],
          "feedback_correct_html": "<p>正确！输入连接器上的电源路径和电源返回路径的额定连续电流必须至少为 100A。</p>",
          "feedback_incorrect_html": "<p>不正确。输入连接器要求主电源和电源返回路径的最小额定值为 100A 连续电流。</p>"
        },
        {
